{
  "day": "1",
  "heading": "Drive from Rohru to Janglik (9,415 ft)",
  "sub_heading": "Drive distance: 40 km | Drive Duration: 3 hours | Pick up point for Indiahikes trekkers: Shaktan Homestay Rohru | Pick up Time: 9.30 am | Location of Indiahikes basecamp: Janglik",
  "details": "Transport will be organised from  Shaktan Homestay Rohru at 9.30 AM. The cost of cab will be Rs. 1150 per trekker (additional 5% GST) for the transfer from Rohru to Janglik. These are non-AC SUV vehicles. Please pre-book your transport through the dashboard before your trek.\n\nNote: Your will receive your rentals and deposit your cloakroom luggage (if any) at Rohru itself."
}

