{
  "day": "7",
  "heading": "Trek from River campsite to Barua. Drive to Shimla.",
  "sub_heading": "Trek Distance: 7.15 km | Trek Duration: 5 hours | Altitude loss:10,745 ft to 7,725 ft | Drive Distance: 207 km | Drive Duration: 6-7 hours | Drop off point: Shimla, ISBT.",
  "details": "Rental and cloakroom returns will take place at Rampur on the way back to Shimla. If you are not opting for Indiahikes Transport, you still need to come to Rampur to collect your cloakroom or return your rental items.\nTransport from Barua to Shimla will be arranged to start at 1.00 PM. You will reach Shimla around 11 pm. The cost of cab will be Rs. 2400 per trekker (additional 5% GST) for the transfer from Barua to Shimla. These are non-AC SUV vehicles.\nPlease note: The distance between campsites may vary by 100 meters depending on weather conditions and your route. The altitude may also vary by 100 feet for similar reasons."
}

{
  "day": "8",
  "heading": "Buffer Day",
  "sub_heading": "This depends completely on the weather conditions on the trek and the call will be taken by the trek leader.",
  "details": "If the buffer day is used,  you have to pay us Rs. 2,500 per day (INR) +5% GST. The money will be collected by the Trek Leader only if we use the buffer day."
}
